quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,64,"Loba: Eh bino bato baye bozua buku! Boya na liloba moko oyo ekosangisa biso na bino ete: Tobondela Nzambe mosusu te sé Allah, mpe tosangisa ye na eloko te, mpe tozua ba Nkolo misusu te na botıki Allah. Soki bapesi mokongo, boloba na bango ete: Bozala banzeneneke ete biso nde tozali bandimi"
  3,65,Eh bino bato bozua buku! Mpona nini bozali kosuana mpona Ibrâhîm? Mpe bino boyebi ete torah mpe indjil mikitaki sé sima naye (Ibrâhîm)? Boye bino bozali kososola te
  3,66,"Tala bino, bozali kosuana na likambo oyo bino boyebi, kasi mpona nini bozali kosuana na likambo oyo boyebi te? Mpe Allah ayebi kasi bino boyebi te"
  3,67,"Ibrâhîm azalaki moyuda mpe moklisto te. Kasi azalaki nde hanifa mondimi, mpe azalaki te elongo na baye basangisaki (Allah)"
  3,68,"Ya sôló bato bakotuta ntolo mpona Ibrâhîm, bazali ba oyo balandaki ye na ntoma oyo (Muhammad) na bandimi. Allah nde azali mobateli ya bandimi"
  3,69,"Lisanga ya bato kati na baye bazwa buku balukaka kopengwisa bino, bakopengwisa sé milimo mia bango moko, nzoka nde bazali koyeba te"
  3,70,Eh bino baye bozua buku! Mpona nini bozali kopengwa na mikapo mia Allah mpe bino bozali banzeneneke
  3,71,"Eh bino baye bozua buku! Mpona nini bozali kosangisa mabe na bosôló, mpe bozali kobomba bosôló mpe bozali na kati ya koyeba"